reviewText: EXPECTED SINGERS SHOWN ON COVER OF THIS DVD TO BE MORE UP BEAT SINGING GOSPEL SONGS,NOTHING ELSE FOR ME TO SAY EXCEPT I WOULD NOT RECOMMEND THIS BVD,HOWEVER I DO REALIZE THAT THERE ARE PEOPLE WHO ENJOY THEIR SINGING.
My family members have been fans of the Canton Spirituals for many years.  This dvd is wonderful!!
Nothing But The Hits is a very good gospel video, I love the Canton Spirituals and I continue to purchase their music.
This is a great gospel, quartet CD. I love the Canton Spirituals! It has some of the best hits on it. You will love it! I recommend it to anyone who enjoys this type of music.
don't waste your money poor recording
I was a little it surprised, because this was not nearly all of their best stuff!
I would disappoint in this video the voice again did not match the video it was separate from speaking and singing
Songs seem laden with disparity, loneliness and sorrow. They seem to morn the loss of the dad, rather than to praise God and celebrate life. This could be just my opinion or personal analogy.
I might be biased cause they've always been my favorite gospel group, but the dvd is great. Different performance from a live show as well as interviews in between
I order this cd for my 75 year old grandpa he was thrilled. I was so happy to see a smile on his face!
My dad enjoys contemporary gospel music and he loved this.

There isn't much left for me to say concerning this group. I am delighted with this DVD.  I am Blessed by this group and their true love for Our Lord and Savior.  I hope to go and see them in service live one day.  But until then I will enjoy and cherish all the cd's and dvd's that I have. God Be With This Group.

Be Blessed... I was

Thia
